title: High school football: Hinsdale Central falls in regular season finale
text:
High school football: Hinsdale Central falls in regular season finale   12:37 a.m. CDT By SUBURBAN LIFE MEDIA 
OAK PARK â€“ Hinsdale Central's football team is assured a Class 8A playoff berth, but the Red Devils could have envisioned a better way to enter the postseason. 
After pulling off a 45-38 overtime win against Hinsdale South on Oct. 16, Central fell 39-7 to Oak Park-River Forest on Oct. 23. 
It was the first time this season Central (7-2, 4-2 West Suburban Silver) was held below 20 points.
